title: Super-NES-Genesis-64 ROM superpack
description:
Here are a good collection of roms from NES, genesis, super nintendo, and n64.
 
To play them you will need an emulator

 look for these decent emulators
 
PJ 64 for nintendo64
 
gens for genesis

jnes for nes

snesgt for super nintendo

sorry i didnt supply them

but they are small downloads and easy to find

sorry about any dupes, its hard to filter them all from thousands of roms

if you have a controller you will be set.
